\par }\pard \s17\qc \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\cs20\i\f1\cf6\insrsid8136756 Job 1:1}{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 
\par }\pard \s17\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 
\par There was a certain man in the land of Ausis, whose name was Job; and than man was true, blameless, righteous, and godly, abstaining from everything evil.}{\insrsid8136756  2 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And he had seven sons and three daughters.}{
\insrsid8136756  3 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And his cattle con
sisted of seven thousand sheep, three thousand camels, five hundred yoke of oxen, five hundred she-asses in the pastures, and a very great household, and he had a great husbandry on the earth; and that man was most noble of the men of the east.}{
