And the Lord said to the devil, Hast thou observe
d by servant Job, that there is none of men upon the earth like him, a harmless, true, blameless godly man, abstaining from all evil? and he yet cleaves to innocence, whereas thou has told me to destroy his substance without cause?}{\insrsid8136756  4 }{
\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And the devil answered and said to the Lord, Skin for skin, all that a man has will he give as a ransom for his life.}{\insrsid8136756  5 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 
