\par And the Lord spoke to Moses face to face, as if one should speak to his friend; and he retired into the camp: but his servant Joshua the son of Naue, a young man, departed not forth from the tabernacle.}{\insrsid8136756  12 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 
And Moses said to the Lord, Lo! thou sayest to me, Lead on this people; but thou hast not shewed me whom thou wilt send with me, but thou hast said to me, I know thee above all, and thou hast favour with me.}{\insrsid8136756  13 }{
\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 If then I have found favour in thy sight, reveal thyself to me, that I may evidently see thee; that I may find favour in thy sight, and that I may know that this great nation is thy people.}{\insrsid8136756  14 }{
\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And he says, I myself will go before thee, and give thee rest.}{\insrsid8136756  15 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And he says to him, If thou go not up with us thyself, bring me not up hence.}{\insrsid8136756  16 }{
\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And how shall it be surely known, that both I and this people have found favour with thee, except only if thou go with us? So both I and thy people shall be glorified beyond all the nations, as many as are upon the earth.}{
\insrsid8136756  17 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And the Lord said to Moses, I will also do for thee this thing, which thou hast spoken; for thou hast found grace before me, and I know thee above all.}{\insrsid8136756  18 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 
And Moses says, Manifest thyself to me.}{\insrsid8136756  19 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And God said, I will pass by before thee with my glory, a
nd I will call by my name, the Lord, before thee; and I will have mercy on whom I will have mercy, and will have pity on whom I will have pity.}{\insrsid8136756  20 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 
And God said, Thou shalt not be able to see my face; for no man shall see my face, and live.}{\insrsid8136756  21 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And the Lord said, Behold, there is a place by me: thou shalt stand upon the rock;}{\insrsid8136756  22 }{
\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 and when my glory shall pass by, then I will put thee into a hole of the rock; and I will cover thee over with my hand, until I shall have passed by.}{\insrsid8136756  23 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And I will remove
 my hand, and then shalt thou see my back parts; but my face shall not appear to thee. 
