And there were born to him seven sons and three daughters.}{\insrsid8136756  14 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And he called the first Day, and the second Casia, and the third Amalthaea's horn.}{\insrsid8136756  15 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 
