\par }\pard \s17\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 
\par And the hand of the Lord came upon me, and the Lord brought me forth by the Spirit, and set me in the midst of the plain, and it was full of human bones.}{\insrsid8136756  2 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 
And he led me round about them every way: and, behold, there were very many on the face of the plain, very dry.}{\insrsid8136756  3 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 
And he said to me, Son of man, will these bones live? and I said, O Lord God, thou knowest this.}{\insrsid8136756  4 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And he said
 to me, Prophesy upon these bones, and thou shalt say to them, Ye dry bones, hear the word of the Lord.}{\insrsid8136756  5 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 Thus saith the Lord to these bones; Behold, I will bring upon you the breath of life:}{
\insrsid8136756  6 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 and I will lay sinews upon you, and will bring up flesh upon you, and will spread skin upon you, and will put my Spirit into you, and ye shall live; and ye shall know that I am the Lord.}{\insrsid8136756 
 7 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 So I prophesied as the Lord commanded me: and it came to pass while I was prophesying, that, behold there was a shaking, and the bones approached each one to his joint.}{\insrsid8136756  8 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 
And I looked, and behold, sinews and flesh grew upon them, and skin came upon them.}{\insrsid8136756  9 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And he said to me, Prophesy to the wind, prophesy, son of man, and
 say to the wind, Thus saith the Lord; Come from the four winds, and breathe upon these dead men, and let them live.}{\insrsid8136756  10 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 
So I prophesied as he commanded me, and the breath entered into them, and they lived, and stood upon their feet, a very great congregation.}{\insrsid8136756  11 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 
And the Lord spoke to me, saying, Son of man, these bones are the whole house of Israel: and they say, Our bones are become dry, our hope has perished, we are quite spent.}{\insrsid8136756  12 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 
therefore prophesy and say, Thus saith the Lord; Behold, I will open your tombs, and will bring you up out of your tombs, and will bring you into the land of Israel.}{\insrsid8136756  13 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 
And ye shall know that I am the Lord, when I have opened your graves, that I may bring up my people from their graves.}{\insrsid8136756  14 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And I will put my Spirit within you, an
d ye shall live, and I will place you upon your own land: and ye shall know that I am the Lord; I have spoken, and will do it, saith the Lord. 
