\par In the beginning God made the heaven and the earth.}{\insrsid8136756  2 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 But the earth was unsightly and unfurnished and darkness was over the deep, and the Spirit of God moved over the water.}{\insrsid8136756  3 }{
\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And God said, Let there be light, and there was light.}{\insrsid8136756  4 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And God saw the light that it was good, and God divided between the light and the darkness.}{\insrsid8136756  5 }{
\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And God called the light Day, and the darkness he called Night, and there was evening and there was morning, the first day.}{\insrsid8136756  6 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 
And God said, Let there be a firmament in the midst of the water, and let it be a division between water and water, and it was so.}{\insrsid8136756  7 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 
And God made the firmament, and God divided between the water which was under the firmament and the water which was above the firmament. }{\insrsid8136756 8.}{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And God called the firmament Heaven, and Go
d saw that it was good, and there was evening and there was morning, the second day.}{\insrsid8136756  9 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 
And God said, Let the water which is under the heaven be collected into one place, and let the dry land appear, and it was so. And the water which was under the heaven was collected into its places, and the dry land appeared.}{\insrsid8136756  10 }{
\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And God called the dry land Earth, and the gatherings of the waters he called Seas, and God saw that it was good.}{\insrsid8136756  11 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 
And God said, Let the earth bring forth the herb of grass bearing seed according to its kind and according to its likeness, and the fruit-tree bearing fruit whose seed in it, according to its kind on the earth, and it was so.}{\insrsid8136756  12 }{
\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And the earth brought forth the herb of grass bearing seed according to its kind and according to its like
ness, and the fruit tree bearing fruit whose seed is in it, according to its kind on the earth, and God saw that it was good.}{\insrsid8136756  13 }{\cs19\f1\fs32\insrsid8136756 And there was evening and there was morning, the third day. 
